divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside helping my daughter with her telescope. We were running randomstar searches and viewing what we could see of the planetary alignment when wenoticed two white objects moving very fast at a high altitude. I called my wifeout and attempted to get a good look through the telescope. I caught a glimpseof one of the vehicles and it was not a satelite or plane. They moved from northto sse at 148 degrees when they suddenly changed course and flew extremely fastto the south. They cleared our view in an incredible amount of time. We haveseen planes and such and these were nothing we had ever seen before. One wastraveling directly behind the other until they changed direction when they wentone above the other.From the time we saw them to the north to the time they wereout of sight was less than a minute and our view was not abstructed by anything.
Summary: Twin , fast moving, high altitude vehicles
